OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fbreezy this evening and overnight with
OL,7,Fshowers mixed with clear spells.
OL,8,FShowers could turn heavy at times and
OL,9,Fmerge to give longer spells of rain
OL,10,Fbefore easing by dawn. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FMostly dry through the
OL,13,Fmorning with sunny spells. A few
OL,14,Fshowers possible in the afternoon
OL,15,Ftowards the south. Feeling pleasant in
OL,16,Fany brighter spells with winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
