OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA spell
OL,6,Fof rain will move through on Friday.
OL,7,FHigh pressure then building in over
OL,8,Fthe weekend to bring a settled picture
OL,9,Fwith sunny spells and lighter winds.
